'''A型主序星(AV星)'''是[[恆星光譜|光譜]]為A，亮度為V，在[[主序帶|主序帶]]（[[氫|氫]]燃燒）上恆星。這些恆星的定義是在[[恆星光譜|恆星光譜]]类型A和光度级V。[[恆星光譜|恆星光譜]]上有強烈的[[巴耳末系|氫的巴耳末吸收譜線]] <ref>[http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/hbase/starlog/staspe.html Stellar Spectral Types] {{Wayback|url=http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/hbase/starlog/staspe.html |date=20090102042431 }}, entry at hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu, accessed on line June 19, 2007.</ref><ref>"An Introduction to Modern Astrophysics" by B.W Caroll and D.A Ostlie 1996 edition, chapter 8</ref>，它們的質量從[[太陽|太陽]]的1.4倍至2.1倍[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]，[[有效溫度|表面溫度]]在7,600至10,000[[熱力學溫標|K]] <ref>[http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1981A&AS...46..193H Empirical bolometric corrections for the main-sequence] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1981A%26AS...46..193H |date=20190717051054 }}, G. M. H. J. Habets and J. R. W. Heintze, ''Astronomy and Astrophysics Supplement'' '''46''' (November 1981), pp. 193–237, Tables VII and VIII.</ref>。

明亮的和附近的A型主序星的例子包括[[牛郎星|牛郎星]](A7 V)、[[天狼星|天狼星A]](A1 V)和[[織女星|織女星]](A0 V)<ref>[[SIMBAD|SIMBAD]], entries on [http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Sirius%20A Sirius A] {{Wayback|url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Sirius%20A |date=20160304130454 }} and [http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Vega Vega] {{Wayback|url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Vega |date=20181021190825 }}, accessed June 19, 2007.</ref>。


== 行星 ==
A型主序星恒星都是年轻的（通常是几亿年），并发射出比单独的恒星发射的红外辐射更多的额外红外辐射。这些过剩的红外辐射的原因是来自于[[岩屑盤|岩屑盤]]的红外辐射，在[[岩屑盤|岩屑盤]]中行星形成<ref name=apj124_1_514>{{citation | display-authors=1 | last1=Song | first1=Inseok | last2=Weinberger | first2=A. J. | last3=Becklin | first3=E. E. | last4=Zuckerman | first4=B. | last5=Chen | first5=C. | title=M-Type Vega-like Stars | journal=The Astronomical Journal | date=2002 | volume=124 | issue=1 | pages=514–518 | doi=10.1086/341164 | bibcode=2002AJ....124..514S | arxiv=astro-ph/0204255 }}</ref>。

